latestPosts.caption:
I wasn’t even planning on buying anything ethnic, but when I came across this pastel kurta set from @172threads, it just caught my eye.

Soft, pretty, easy to wear! It’s giving dreamy festive outfit vibes in all the best ways 🌸

Perfect for the upcoming festive season, whether it’s Rakhi, Ganesh Chaturthi, or small family gatherings when you want to stay ethnic but fresh.

Styled it with minimal jewellery, silver juttis, and that clean girl glow ✨ Didn’t want to overdo it because the outfit already speaks for itself.

Let me know your thoughts on the styling, and go check out their page because they’ve got some amazing collection at super affordable prices!
